# Web Dashboard Rules

## Architecture
- Use Server Components by default; add "use client" only when needed
- Data fetching: use fetch() in Server Components, not useEffect
- Auth: check session server-side in layout.tsx using Supabase SSR

## UI
- Use shadcn/ui primitives — do not build custom UI atoms from scratch
- All colours via Tailwind CSS variables — no inline hex values
- Dark mode first — use dark: variant only for light mode overrides

## State
- Prefer URL state (searchParams) over client state where possible
- Use Zustand only for global client state (auth, payment status)
